01:19:36.360 --> 01:19:38.328
Well, please come up.

01:19:45.480 --> 01:19:48.290
Could you keep an eye
on that for me, please?

01:20:02.000 --> 01:20:03.161
Do you think we should hug?

01:20:03.240 --> 01:20:04.844
